t: "Ko sabu firtugol ma…ď…ďe ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin Men Hu…óirnoo …ďe, Men Wa…ói …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yooru…óe : hi…ďe waylita konngol ngol gaay e nokku maggol, …ďe yejjiti ge…ďal e kon ko …ďe anndintinanoo e mun. A seerataa hi…óa ∆īellitoo e dow janfa iwruka e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa see…óaa…ďe e ma…ď…ďe.Yaafano …ďe laa…ďanaa […ďe]. Pellet, Alla no Yi…ói mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"